{"tid":748502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際研究香港】香港與加泰隆尼亞","createTime":"2018-07-19T09:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T09:35:08.000Z","uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21da2404add34135bc254d894b82a90410a8d542","tid":748502,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/1769579999830116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbrianfonghk%2Fposts%2F1769579999830116&d=ZLe4iOmHm5XT7L3rTUyYzUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eafb906f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/1769579999830116</a><br />\n<br />\n近年，本土運動興起，令香港政治在比較研究上日益重要。加拿大學者Andr&eacute; Lecours和Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Dupr&eacute;剛在《Ethnicities》發表研究文章，就比較了香港和加泰隆尼亞，指出兩地近年都因為溫和自治訴求被中央打壓，因而出現自決分離呼聲。但由於兩地政制不同，民主政制下的加泰，其自決分離運動轉化為加泰地方政府和馬德里中央政府的衝突；<span style=\"color: red;\">而在局部民主政制下的香港，其自決分離運動則被限制在公民社會，成為挑戰包括中央和香港特區政府的在野力量。</span>文章相當精采，不可不讀。<br />\n<br />\n論文：<a href=\"https://sci-hub.tw/10.1177/1468796818785937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsci-hub.tw%2F10.1177%2F1468796818785937&d=ZLe4iOmHm5XT7L3rTUyYzUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e26a16de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sci-hub.tw/10.1177/1468796818785937</a>"},{"pid":"ca1c14c9e7c37035b7819e949b31eb34e58f5936","tid":748502,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"615aaa5933e4ca6744fbf55f0de62605f393ee26","tid":748502,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"249985a2c2f310d5e538793984a36cbd8fc85425","tid":748502,"uid":133272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"too long later read"},{"pid":"90925534ef702a9ece674c75dc424f71785a37de","tid":748502,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":